donor_name: FOOD AND AGRICULTURE ORGANIZATION OF THE
outputs.output_descr: Strengthening Capacity for Good Governance in Swaziland to build capacity for transparency and accountability through systematic planning, monitoring and evaluation in national institutions. Institutional strengthening will also be built to increase access to justice and law as well adherence on human right at all levels. Building of and information dissemination as well as promotion of its use will be enhanced in the implementation of the project  to facilitate opening of space for dialogues on provision of fundamental rights  and associated services to the vulnerable groups and individuals.
